results.deck: Jellyvision is a game development company best known for "You Don't Know Jack" games.
results.description:
Jellyvision was founded back in 1989, and is best known for developing the "You Don't Know Jack" games. 
 
Jellyvision has finally released their newest entry into the "You Don't Know Jack" series with "You Don't know Jack" (2011) for the Xbox 360, Playstation 3, Wii, Nintendo DS, and PC. Jellyvision has said that they have planned DLC down the road for "You Don't Know Jack."
